1
00:00:42,666 --> 00:00:45,869
The infinite expanse ofthe universe...

2
00:00:46,866 --> 00:00:50,369
A place filled with silence and light...

3
00:00:52,766 --> 00:00:58,171
Our Solar System is about
30,OOO light years away

4
00:00:58,166 --> 00:01:02,436
from the Galactic Center.

5
00:01:25,566 --> 00:01:26,900
Earth.

6
00:01:28,166 --> 00:01:32,069
The planet that, like a mother,
gave birth to us and raised us.

7
00:01:35,833 --> 00:01:38,335
At the center ofthe Milky Way,

8
00:01:38,333 --> 00:01:42,704
there is a space-time void with a mass
two million times that of our sun:

9
00:01:42,700 --> 00:01:45,436
