10
00:01:46,833 --> 00:01:48,201
A black hole...

11
00:01:49,299 --> 00:01:52,336
A pitch-black hole whose grasp not even
the slightest ray of light can escape.

12
00:01:52,333 --> 00:01:57,538
The density in the deepest parts ofthat
hole makes it so gravity is infinite.

13
