contains information about the
matter that was sucked in.

17
00:02:23,866 --> 00:02:28,136
Even in the 23rd century,

18
00:02:28,133 --> 00:02:32,770
black holes remain a phenomenon
unfathomable to mankind.

19
00:02:33,066 --> 00:02:37,003
Thus, humanity is still not aware that black holes are
the true rulers ofthe space-time continuum.

20
00:02:37,000 --> 00:02:44,173
No one has yet realized that
they are sentient life forms.

21
00:02:47,066 --> 00:02:51,003
Like a young lion approaching
humans in the savanna,

22
00:02:50,966 --> 00:02:54,235
feigning curiosity at first,

23
00:02:54,233 --> 00:02:58,370
and then reacting in a
completely di_erent way...

24
00:02:59,400 --> 00:03:03,103
Earth was suddenly faced
with a black hole.

25
00:03:04,233 --> 00:03:06,401
Space Battleship Yamato.

26
00:03:06,366 --> 00:03:11,003
17 years have passed since it sunk into the seas of
the migrating planet Aquarius.

27
00:03:11,666 --> 00:03:14,869
lt is the year 2220 AD.

28
00:03:14,833 --> 00:03:18,670
On Earth, mankind is confronted with an unprecedented
crisis:

29
00:03:19,699 --> 00:03:24,838
a dark stellar body with a gravity so enormous not a
single ray of light can escape,

30
00:03:24,833 --> 00:03:26,334
a black hole.

31
00:03:27,199 --> 00:03:33,606
Every second, the black hole, hailing from a distant
corner ofthe galaxy, gets closer to Earth.

32
00:04:49,366 --> 00:04:51,367
Gravitational signatures
detected at 12 o'clock!

33
00:04:51,600 --> 00:04:53,868
Distance: approximately 25 space km!

34
