l have never seen ships like that before.

36
00:05:16,966 --> 00:05:18,567
How many ships are there?

37
00:05:18,566 --> 00:05:21,235
We have detected about
900 and counting.

38
00:05:21,199 --> 00:05:23,201
900?!

39
00:05:23,199 --> 00:05:24,134
