Warp!

54
00:07:28,766 --> 00:07:29,733
Captain Kodai!

55
00:07:47,533 --> 00:07:49,368
forfreighter Yuki.

56
00:07:49,366 --> 00:07:50,533
Yes.

57
00:07:50,533 --> 00:07:51,667
Here you go.

58
00:07:55,866 --> 00:07:56,600
Captain!

