Shipwreck detected!

68
00:08:41,566 --> 00:08:42,833
Where's that shipwreck?

69
00:08:42,833 --> 00:08:46,770
According to the map, it's 150
space km away at 4 o'clock.

70
00:08:47,166 --> 00:08:49,935
We'll rescue the survivors.

71
00:08:49,933 --> 00:08:52,001
Engine at full power!

72
