Going full power with
this shabby engine...

73
00:08:54,266 --> 00:08:55,867
this has got to be a joke!

74
00:08:55,866 --> 00:08:57,901
Shut up and do it!

75
00:08:57,899 --> 00:08:59,434
How long have you been on this ship?!

76
00:08:59,433 --> 00:09:00,233
R-Right.

77
00:09:00,233 --> 00:09:01,767
Full powerforward!

78
