A survivor?

81
00:09:33,666 --> 00:09:35,200
Looks like the barrier isn't broken.

82
00:09:35,833 --> 00:09:36,934
Help him.

83
00:09:39,466 --> 00:09:40,567
Damn!

84
00:09:41,966 --> 00:09:43,434
You will pay for this!

85
00:09:43,433 --> 00:09:43,966
Wait!

86
00:09:43,933 --> 00:09:44,466
We're allies!

87
00:09:44,466 --> 00:09:45,800
Allies?

88
00:09:45,766 --> 00:09:47,067
H-Hey!

89
00:09:47,366 --> 00:09:48,600
Emigrant ships from Earth?

90
00:09:48,600 --> 00:09:49,701
Right.

91
00:09:49,700 --> 00:09:55,338
l was part of an escort fleet
transporting 300 million people to Amarl.

92
00:09:55,733 --> 00:09:57,401
300 million people?!

93
00:10:02,500 --> 00:10:03,701
Were you attacked by them?

94
00:10:03,733 --> 00:10:05,101
Y-Yes!

95
00:10:05,100 --> 00:10:05,533
Damn!

96
00:10:06,333 --> 00:10:07,567
Move!

97
00:10:08,266 --> 00:10:11,035
All right, she can still fly.

98
00:10:11,033 --> 00:10:13,168
Sakurai, locate the enemy's position.

99
00:10:13,133 --> 00:10:13,500
Roger.

100
00:10:13,833 --> 00:10:15,234
Damn them...

101
00:10:15,933 --> 00:10:16,800
Wait!

102
00:10:16,799 --> 00:10:17,867
Don't shoot yet!

103
00:10:18,766 --> 00:10:19,800
Here they come.

104
00:10:20,033 --> 00:10:21,834
Grab on to something!

105
00:10:31,233 --> 00:10:32,767
What's your name?

106
00:10:33,066 --> 00:10:37,270
Earth Defense Force 1st Lieutenant
and Tactical Oflicer Kamijou Ryo.

107
00:10:37,733 --> 00:10:40,435
Kamijou, prepare the main battery!

108
00:10:41,933 --> 00:10:43,734
Preparing main battery.

109
00:10:43,733 --> 00:10:45,334
D-Distance: 3000!

110
00:10:45,333 --> 00:10:46,967
C-Captain! We're going to collide!

111
00:10:46,933 --> 00:10:48,467
Keep your cool, Sakurai!

112
00:10:57,733 --> 00:10:58,500
We're going to crash!

113
00:11:07,566 --> 00:11:08,566
Full throttle!

114
00:11:21,566 --> 00:11:23,000
Now! Fire!

115
00:11:23,000 --> 00:11:24,468
Firing main battey!

116
