We did it!

117
00:11:31,966 --> 00:11:34,068
Well done, Kamijou.

118
00:11:34,033 --> 00:11:34,800
You've got some skill.

119
00:11:34,799 --> 00:11:36,234
That's Captain Kodai for you!

120
00:11:36,233 --> 00:11:38,001
Well done.

121
00:11:38,000 --> 00:11:39,768
Captain Kodai...

122
00:11:39,766 --> 00:11:42,568
The legenday captain of the Yamato...

123
00:11:42,833 --> 00:11:44,601
We'll head back to Earth immediately.

124
