That's why l've been waiting for you.

202
00:17:12,466 --> 00:17:13,500
For me?

203
00:17:14,133 --> 00:17:19,538
l want you to take command ofthe Third Emigration
Fleet escort forces.

204
00:17:19,533 --> 00:17:22,736
You're the only one
who can save mankind.

205
