However, Yuki knew that you'd take
responsibility in this crisis

209
00:17:42,299 --> 00:17:47,638
and assumed command o1the
First Emigration Fleet.

210
00:17:49,200 --> 00:17:50,134
Miyuki...

211
00:17:50,833 --> 00:17:54,303
Does she know about the
First Emigration Fleet?

212
00:18:45,000 --> 00:18:47,602
''Dear, how is space?

213
00:18:47,866 --> 00:18:50,335
The universe is your sea, isn't it?''

214
00:18:51,200 --> 00:18:52,701
So you've returned...

215
00:18:55,733 --> 00:18:57,768
Welcome back, Miyuki.

216
00:19:13,799 --> 00:19:14,500
Your motherEUR''

217
00:19:14,466 --> 00:19:16,167
lt's your fault, Father.

218
00:19:16,766 --> 00:19:18,067
Th-That's not true.

219
00:19:18,066 --> 00:19:20,768
You're way too attached to the Yamato.

220
00:19:20,733 --> 00:19:24,303
The Yamato has already
sunk, don't you get it?

221
00:19:24,299 --> 00:19:25,734
lt's resting in the depths ofthat sea.

222
00:19:28,566 --> 00:19:30,167
Yes.

223
00:19:30,166 --> 00:19:33,802
Mom just pretended to understand.

224
00:19:35,200 --> 00:19:38,536
ln truth, she was so lonely.

225
00:19:38,533 --> 00:19:43,838
ln my memories, her smile was
always veiled by loneliness.

226
00:19:49,666 --> 00:19:52,001
l wantto see mom.

227
00:19:52,533 --> 00:19:55,903
Miyuki, l haven't given up on her!

228
00:19:59,200 --> 00:20:00,334
Kodai here.

229
00:20:00,866 --> 00:20:02,300
We have an emergency!

230
00:20:02,299 --> 00:20:05,469
The Second Emigration Fleet has been attacked by
an unknown armada.

231
00:20:05,433 --> 00:20:06,801
We've lost contact with them!

232
00:20:07,366 --> 00:20:08,200
Understood.

233
00:20:08,200 --> 00:20:09,134
l'll be right there.

234
00:20:13,966 --> 00:20:15,000
Just go.

235
00:20:15,700 --> 00:20:16,567
l'm sorry.

236
00:20:51,266 --> 00:20:53,735
So the Second Fleet was
annihilated as well...

237
00:20:54,333 --> 00:20:59,171
Both the First and Second fleet
were attacked in the same vicinity,

238
00:20:59,166 --> 00:21:01,167
a region about 17,OOO light
years away from Earth.

239
00:21:01,633 --> 00:21:04,702
lt's as ifthey were ambushed.

240
00:21:05,299 --> 00:21:08,436
There's one more thing bothering me.

241
00:21:08,400 --> 00:21:11,903
The enemy fleet was diflerent
from the one l've encountered.

242
00:21:11,900 --> 00:21:13,768
Theirform is too di_erent.

