to prevent the emigration.

246
00:21:41,766 --> 00:21:45,870
Please allow me to command
the Third Emigration Fleet.

247
00:21:47,500 --> 00:21:49,168
Thanks, Kodai.

248
00:21:50,366 --> 00:21:53,902
ForYuki, for mankind...

249
00:21:55,633 --> 00:21:58,202
Your ship is ready foryou.

250
00:22:00,433 --> 00:22:02,201
lt's the Space Battleship Yamato.

251
00:22:03,166 --> 00:22:04,133
The Yamato?!

252
00:22:07,299 --> 00:22:11,604
Space Battleship Yamato
is awaiting your return.

253
00:22:19,299 --> 00:22:21,335
Aquarius.

254
00:22:21,333 --> 00:22:22,967
17 years ago...

255
00:22:22,933 --> 00:22:27,904
the migrating planet Aquarius
threatened to flood the Earth.

256
00:22:38,333 --> 00:22:40,234
Kodai, Yuki.

257
00:22:40,233 --> 00:22:42,101
You two will have a wonde_ul child.

