00:22:45,599 --> 00:22:49,070
l'll think of it as my grandchild.

260
00:23:20,366 --> 00:23:21,900
Mother Earth...

261
00:23:21,900 --> 00:23:24,702
Take care ofthese kids.

262
00:23:25,833 --> 00:23:27,367
Yamato...

263
00:23:28,166 --> 00:23:32,737
You have lought and
perished for this planet.

264
00:23:32,733 --> 00:23:35,836
