732
01:04:15,699 --> 01:04:20,104
Actually, my current duties were supposed to
be handled by Commander Kodai.

733
01:04:22,699 --> 01:04:27,271
We were busy trying to warp out and
escape underfierce enemy fire.

734
01:04:27,233 --> 01:04:30,769
The ship she boarded warped
without a person on board.

735
01:04:30,766 --> 01:04:32,067
Oh, where is it?

736
01:04:34,033 --> 01:04:35,401
lt's this ship.

737
01:04:58,833 --> 01:05:01,035
So you couldn't find her body...

738
01:05:01,033 --> 01:05:01,433
Yes.

739
01:05:02,366 --> 01:05:03,700
l see.

740
01:05:03,699 --> 01:05:06,135
