748
01:05:35,500 --> 01:05:37,535
Without that resolve,

749
01:05:37,533 --> 01:05:41,403
it would mean that mankind
has merely run away from it.

750
01:05:44,500 --> 01:05:45,667
Chief Sanada!

751
01:05:45,633 --> 01:05:48,102
We have received a message
from Captain Kodai.

752
01:05:49,433 --> 01:05:52,202
We have landed on Amarl.

753
01:05:52,199 --> 01:05:56,270
April 5th, 14:10 Earth time.

754
01:05:56,266 --> 01:05:57,967
The situation is as follows:

755
01:05:58,500 --> 01:06:01,069
